## üåó DARK MODE SUPPORT

All colors automatically adapt to dark/light mode. The `adaptiveColor()` helper handles this:

```swift
// Light mode: #1A1A1A, Dark mode: #FFFFFF
static let primary = adaptiveColor(light: "1A1A1A", dark: "FFFFFF")
```

